results.assertion_string:
not prioritise(let id__ = 0
               within stm0::D__(id__) [[tock <- tock, tock <- tock']],
               <diff(Events, {tock', tock}), {tock}>)
    \ {tock}
        :[divergence free [FD]]

not RUN({tock}) ||| CHAOS(diff(Events, {|tock|}))
        [F= let id__ = 0 within stm0::D__(id__)
not let id__ = 0 within stm0::D__(id__) :[deadlock free]
let id__ = 0 within stm0::D__(id__) ; RUN({r__}) :[deadlock free]
